---
import ProjectLayout from "../../components/ProjectLayout.astro";
import TechIcon from "../../components/TechIcon.astro";
---

<ProjectLayout
  title="ImmoScout24 Austria — Search Platform"
  description="Case study: contributing to Austria's top 3 real estate search platform with fully tested distributed microservices"
>
  <main>
    <section
      class="project-hero"
      style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1 0%, #ec4899 100%); color: white; padding: 64px 0 48px; margin-bottom: 3rem; text-align: center; margin-top: 3rem;"
    >
      <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px;">
        <h1
          style="font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: white !important; text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); background: none !important; -webkit-text-fill-color: white !important;"
        >
          ImmoScout24 Austria
        </h1>
        <p
          style="font-size: 1.35rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; line-height: 1.6;"
        >
          Contributing to a top 3 real estate search platform in Austria —
          with enterprise-grade SSO, fully tested distributed services, and marketing automation
        </p>
        <div
          style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;"
        >
          <span
            style="padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-radius: 50px; font-weight: 600; backdrop-filter: blur(10px);"
          >
            LIVE
          </span>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/calindotgabriel/immobile-search"
            style="padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); color: #6366f1; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.3s ease;"
          >
            View on GitHub
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <article style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px;">

      <!-- THE PROBLEM -->
      <section
        class="content-section"
        style="background: var(--gradient-card); border-radius: 20px; padding: 3rem 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);"
      >
        <h2
          style="font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--dark);"
        >
          The Problem
        </h2>
        <p
          style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--gray); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;"
        >
          ImmoScout24 is one of the top 3 most-searched real estate platforms in Austria,
          part of the Scout24 group headquartered in Germany. The Austrian branch needed to
          keep pace with the parent organization's engineering standards while evolving its
          own product — improving user experience, driving organic traffic, and adding marketing
          automation capabilities.
        </p>
        <p
          style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--gray);"
        >
          The existing system was a highly qualitative distributed architecture with
          comprehensive e2e, unit, and integration test coverage. The bar was high:
          every change had to pass through rigorous testing pipelines. Any new feature
          or optimization needed to work within this quality-first culture — not around it.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- THE CHALLENGE -->
      <section
        class="content-section"
        style="background: var(--gradient-card); border-radius: 20px; padding: 3rem 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);"
      >
        <h2
          style="font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--dark);"
        >
          My Biggest Challenge
        </h2>
        <p
          style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--gray); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;"
        >
          Adapting to the quality expectations of a DAX-listed organization was the steepest
          learning curve. The codebase was fully tested at every layer — e2e, integration,
          and unit — across distributed microservices with SSO federated from Scout24's
          main German organization. Nothing shipped without full coverage.
        </p>
        <p
          style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--gray);"
        >
          I had to level up my testing discipline fast, learn to communicate more precisely
          with senior engineers, and develop the habit of syncing with my mentor at the
          moments that actually counted — not too early (wasting their time) and not too
          late (blocking my own progress). That calibration was as valuable as any technical skill.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- WHAT I DELIVERED -->
      <section
        class="content-section"
        style="background: var(--gradient-card); border-radius: 20px; padding: 3rem 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);"
      >
        <h2
          style="font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: var(--dark);"
        >
          What I Delivered
        </h2>

        <div
          class="features-grid"
          style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem;"
        >
          <div
            style="padding: 2rem; background: rgba(99,102,241,0.03); border-radius: 16px; border: 1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.08);"
          >
            <h3
              style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--primary);"
            >
              UX Improvements
            </h3>
            <p style="color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">
              Drove user experience improvements across the search and listing flows,
              making the platform faster to navigate and easier to convert on — directly
              contributing to higher engagement metrics.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            style="padding: 2rem; background: rgba(99,102,241,0.03); border-radius: 16px; border: 1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.08);"
          >
            <h3
              style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--primary);"
            >
              SEO to All-Time High
            </h3>
            <p style="color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">
              Implemented technical SEO optimizations that pushed organic search
              performance to its highest levels in the platform's history — more
              visibility means more listings, more agents, more revenue.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            style="padding: 2rem; background: rgba(99,102,241,0.03); border-radius: 16px; border: 1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.08);"
          >
            <h3
              style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--primary);"
            >
              Marketing Automation (Iterable)
            </h3>
            <p style="color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">
              Integrated Iterable for marketing automation, enabling the business
              to run targeted campaigns, automate lead nurturing, and re-engage
              users — turning traffic into measurable pipeline.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            style="padding: 2rem; background: rgba(99,102,241,0.03); border-radius: 16px; border: 1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.08);"
          >
            <h3
              style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--primary);"
            >
              Enricher Task Upgrades
            </h3>
            <p style="color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">
              Upgraded the functional programming-style enricher tasks that
              process and transform property data — improving reliability
              and maintainability of the data pipeline.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- BUSINESS IMPACT -->
      <section
        class="content-section"
        style="background: var(--gradient-card); border-radius: 20px; padding: 3rem 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);"
      >
        <h2
          style="font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--dark);"
        >
          Business Impact
        </h2>

        <div
          class="metrics-grid"
          style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; margin: 2.5rem 0;"
        >
          <div
            style="text-align: center; padding: 1.5rem; background: rgba(99,102,241,0.05); border-radius: 16px; border: 1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.1);"
          >
            <div
              style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"
            >
              Top 3
            </div>
            <div style="color: var(--gray); font-weight: 500;">
              Most-Used Listing Platform in AT
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            style="text-align: center; padding: 1.5rem; background: rgba(99,102,241,0.05); border-radius: 16px; border: 1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.1);"
          >
            <div
              style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"
            >
              ATH
            </div>
            <div style="color: var(--gray); font-weight: 500;">
              SEO Performance — All-Time High
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            style="text-align: center; padding: 1.5rem; background: rgba(99,102,241,0.05); border-radius: 16px; border: 1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.1);"
          >
            <div
              style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"
            >
              20%
            </div>
            <div style="color: var(--gray); font-weight: 500;">
              Higher User Engagement
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p
          style="font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--gray); margin-top: 1.5rem;"
        >
          These weren't isolated technical wins. Higher SEO meant more organic traffic, which
          meant more listings and agents on the platform. Better UX meant users stayed longer
          and converted more. Iterable meant the business could nurture leads without engineering
          involvement. Every improvement compounded into platform growth.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- WHAT I LEARNED -->
      <section
        class="content-section"
        style="background: var(--gradient-card); border-radius: 20px; padding: 3rem 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);"
      >
        <h2
          style="font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--dark);"
        >
          What I Took Away
        </h2>
        <p
          style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--gray); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;"
        >
          This project fundamentally shaped how I work. I learned that quality isn't a
          phase — it's the speed. A fully tested distributed system doesn't slow you down,
          it gives you the confidence to move fast without breaking things. That mindset
          stayed with me in every project since.
        </p>
        <p
          style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--gray);"
        >
          On the human side, I learned when to reach out to a mentor and when to push
          through on my own. That calibration — knowing when to sync and when to execute —
          is something I now consider a core part of how I operate in any team.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- TECH STACK -->
      <section
        class="content-section"
        style="background: var(--gradient-card); border-radius: 20px; padding: 3rem 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);"
      >
        <h2
          style="font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: var(--dark);"
        >
          Technology Stack
        </h2>
        <div
          style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(140px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;"
        >
          {
            [
              { name: "React", tech: "React" },
              { name: "Hapi.js", tech: "Hapi" },
              { name: "Node.js", tech: "Node.js" },
              { name: "MongoDB", tech: "MongoDB" },
              { name: "AWS", tech: "AWS" },
              { name: "Iterable", tech: "JavaScript" },
            ].map((item) => (
              <div style="padding: 1.25rem 1rem; background: rgba(99,102,241,0.1); color: var(--primary); border-radius: 16px; font-weight: 600; text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.2); transition: all 0.3s ease; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; min-height: 100px; justify-content: center;">
                <TechIcon technology={item.tech} size={32} />
                <span style="font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.2;">
                  {item.name}
                </span>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </section>
    </article>
  </main>
</ProjectLayout>

<style>
  .project-hero h1 {
    color: white !important;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    background: none !important;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: white !important;
    background-clip: initial !important;
  }

  .content-section {
    animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease forwards;
  }

  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .features-grid > div:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .content-section div[style*="min-height: 100px"]:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.15);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .project-hero {
      padding: 48px 0 32px;
    }

    .project-hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.25rem;
    }

    .project-hero p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .content-section {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .metrics-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .content-section div[style*="repeat(auto-fill, minmax(140px, 1fr))"] {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(110px, 1fr)) !important;
      gap: 1rem !important;
    }

    .content-section div[style*="min-height: 100px"] {
      min-height: 80px !important;
      padding: 1rem 0.75rem !important;
    }

    .content-section div[style*="min-height: 100px"] span:first-child {
      font-size: 1.5rem !important;
    }

    .content-section div[style*="min-height: 100px"] span:last-child {
      font-size: 0.8rem !important;
    }
  }
</style>
